  "date": "2026-01-29 05:19:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=555e3ee6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWUHicUbONQZ9KH1ptYX7L1ZcPqqnnhBrhtdDKJLyoeS3VicHnQMEKcgnA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 24px 40px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近我见到人就推荐Clawdbot。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我常常跟人讲：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">凡是能在电脑上完成的事情，都可以被Cladue Code自动完成</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Clawdbot就是一个最好的例证——只要给它一台电脑、权限给到最大，它还真的啥都能干，妥妥的7x24的数字牛马。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我用到Clawdbot的场景算比较中规中矩，已经能够感受到生活有巨大的不同。有的老外玩的花，还让Clawdbot自己去炒股，还真赚钱了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是我们最接近《钢铁侠》里的贾维斯的一次。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Clawdbot不是泡沫，真正的泡沫是这波Mac Mini行情。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Clawdbot最近把Mac Mini带火了，好多人跟风花4000元去抢购Mac Mini，搞得全网都有点缺货了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">真希望我可以早点告诉他们：你的Clawdbot和我的一样，只不过你多花了4000元……</span></strong></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5648148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017317\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23e05f44&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWyX8AUEHJatuWJnCSwsdsIFcTIlDibO5pvVdKVNBJTRFecKmx11z5vDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017319\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=84bc1bdf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWK3goibkR04512xN5WwliaLkX5YxWVmryt85iaX3FkMPyNXMqHh09ic3unA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从原理上讲：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Mac系统本质上只是Linux/Unix套壳，我们直接租云端的Linux VPS(虚拟电脑)就可以了，每个月只要几十块钱。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我用的是腾讯云，一个月20元。也可以用阿里云、火山云、其他的LInux VPS。有的厂商还有优惠，前几个月不要钱。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">只提醒一点：选用海外的服务器，这样网络方面可以方便一些。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100017318\" data-ratio=\"0.5861111111111111\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=10cc1468&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWeiaQmlCYFMCgrQT1WXBUqTscUTQDhyPL4UfjxnZjnja6yTJrx5ECLMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">选择CPU核心不少于2核、内存不小于2G的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我截图这个月，一个月才20.4元。如果要安装桌面，建议内存4G起。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.34444444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b135868b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyW0onibWVrCCnzVejvlslUJ2hARBU8KJmZzsibOvO8As1J3q9Sb8jpQiaag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要担心资源不够用。实测2核2G、2核4G都够用。下面是我的腾讯云VPS过去一天的资源占用情况。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22407407407407406\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017315\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8e0ebebc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWmY2Z1fqiceFgY98O0zWztiawwq6SLOsyJ9L7z9UxvSwgicNdBuuw8rBtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用Linux VPS跑Clawdbot，除了省钱，还有额外的好处：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 20px 0px;padding-left: 28px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">永久在线、网络环境比你好</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">稳定性强</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">虚拟机，不怕搞坏</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0px;font-size: 17px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不需要科学上网，因为本来就是海外的VPS</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你不喜欢黑乎乎的命令行，更喜欢可视化界面，那也没问题，Linux也是可以装上桌面的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我给我的Linux安装了一个最简单的桌面XFCE，还可以通过我的Macbook/Windows，通过“远程桌面”的方式连接它</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017333\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83afd274&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWybCbNUmaSXgeAqSlereTFgaaslly0bMVicDmCb483TU7M4ibQ46aLc4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h1 style=\"font-size: 32px;font-weight: 600;margin: 36px 0px 18px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(233, 125, 91) 50%, rgb(204, 139, 122) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.2 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">给Clawdbot配一台永远在线的电脑</span></h1>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">腾讯云可以一键部署MoltBot(ClawdBot)了</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">选择最便宜的套餐即可</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">执行</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 8px;margin:24px 0px;overflow:hidden;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\">moltbot onboard --install-daemon</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">接受一些霸王条款“我理解非常有风险”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">后面跟着指引就能配置完成，如果英文不好，自己想办法翻译一下即可。Clawdbot指引做得很好，就算是没有技术功底的人，也不需要看自媒体博主的二手指导。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8351851851851851\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017322\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a2812232&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyW8BUibMFkLl1kQFKME74gHC75RluiakEXBA3fFbJI7Sq6y4QXpWicYspww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">默认推荐是用Telegram进行沟通。按照Clawdbot的指引，很快就无痛配置好了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1731481481481483\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017324\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dea80579&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlG7YcMPYTh8ialORvOHRlgyWdnLRscWQJnLEvoVVN525WwQXKSMusDVXCZEKhdG9TxxjCLdTjFdtRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">默认的Telegram实在是不好用，因为我的工作和生活都不在Telegram上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">考虑到主要是想给工作提效，我给Clawdbot(moltbot)配置了飞书。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于具体怎么配置飞书？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我哪儿知道，我让Clawdbot自己给自己配置的</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 8px;margin:24px 0px;overflow:hidden;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/m1heng/clawdbot-fe